PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780743771
OL,3,CMan jailed for 26 years for
OL,4,C'ferocious' knife attack on ex-partner
OL,5,Cat workplace
OL,7,FA 39-year-old man who stabbed his ex-
OL,8,Fpartner 17 times in a "ferocious"
OL,9,Fknife attack at the office building
OL,10,Fwhere she worked after becoming
OL,11,F"obsessed" that she was cheating on
OL,12,Fhim has been jailed for 26 years.
OL,14,FAnwar Ashraf was convicted after a
OL,15,Ftrial at Winchester Crown Court
OL,16,Ffollowing the attack on Carla Skeites
OL,17,Fusing a kitchen knife which happened
OL,18,Fat the premises 3600 Parkway in
OL,19,FWhiteley, Hampshire, at about 9am on
OL,20,FApril 30 2025.
OL,26,@pD@WOUpD@aO]sD@AOUsD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780743771
OL,3,CMan jailed for 26 years for
OL,4,C'ferocious' knife attack on ex-partner
OL,5,Cat workplace
OL,7,FHe had previously pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Fwounding with intent to cause grievous
OL,9,Fbodily harm and possession of a knife
OL,10,Fbut he had denied that he wanted to
OL,11,Fkill her.
OL,13,FThe court heard that the defendant, of
OL,14,FSouthsea, had told police after the
OL,15,Fattack: "What would you do if your
OL,16,Fpartner cheated on you? How would you
OL,17,Freact?"
OL,26,@wD@IOUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780743771
OL,3,CMan jailed for 26 years for
OL,4,C'ferocious' knife attack on ex-partner
OL,5,Cat workplace
OL,7,FJudge Paul Dugdale imposed an extended
OL,8,Fsentence on Ashra with a five-year
OL,9,Fperiod on licence once released from
OL,10,Fcustody and issued a restraining order
OL,11,Ffor life.
OL,13,FHe told him: "You carried out what can
OL,14,Fonly be described as an horrific,
OL,15,Fferocious attack on her and it is the
OL,16,Flevel of ferocity that causes this
OL,17,Fcourt real concern."
OL,26,@uD@NOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780743771
OL,3,CMan jailed for 26 years for
OL,4,C'ferocious' knife attack on ex-partner
OL,5,Cat workplace
OL,7,FHe added: "It's a miracle that she
OL,8,Fsurvived, it's not clear if she will
OL,9,Fever be near to how she was before and
OL,10,Fit's not clear if the pain she suffers
OL,11,Fevery day will go away."
OL,13,FAddressing Ashraf, who the court heard
OL,14,Fhad a drinking problem and was
OL,15,Fsuffering from a mental health crisis,
OL,16,Fhe added: "It's all very well talking
OL,17,Fabout alcohol addiction and addictions
OL,18,Fbut we have to take responsibility for
OL,19,Four actions.
OL,26,@oD@KOUsD@XO]xD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780743771
OL,3,CMan jailed for 26 years for
OL,4,C'ferocious' knife attack on ex-partner
OL,5,Cat workplace
OL,7,F"You knew the effects it could have on
OL,8,Fyou and the effects have been
OL,9,Fdevastating."
OL,11,FIn a victim impact statement read to
OL,12,Fthe court, Ms Skeites said she still
OL,13,Fsuffered flashbacks and nightmares and
OL,14,Fwas undergoing counselling for anxiety.
OL,16,FShe described being in hospital in 10
OL,17,Fdays following the attack and not
OL,18,Fknowing if she would survive the
OL,19,Femergency surgery.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780743771
OL,3,CMan jailed for 26 years for
OL,4,C'ferocious' knife attack on ex-partner
OL,5,Cat workplace
OL,7,FMs Skeites said: "Asking the question
OL,8,Fto the many amazing medics 'Am I going
OL,9,Fto die?' and not getting told the
OL,10,Fanswer you need to hear in that moment
OL,11,Fbut being told 'We are doing
OL,12,Feverything we can for you'.
OL,14,F"The reality hit me that I may not
OL,15,Fhave woken up from surgery."
OL,17,FShe continued : "I find myself not
OL,18,Fbeing able to trust people and I now
OL,19,Fquestion whether they will harm me too.
OL,26,@oD@ROUvD@AOUwD@\O]yD@QOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780743771
OL,3,CMan jailed for 26 years for
OL,4,C'ferocious' knife attack on ex-partner
OL,5,Cat workplace
OL,7,F"Right now I wish I could escape it
OL,8,Fall."
OL,10,FMs Skeites added: "I know I should
OL,11,Fhate Ash for what he has done, maybe
OL,12,Fin time I will but right now I feel
OL,13,Fmore sadness than hate.
OL,15,F"I feel sad that he felt his only
OL,16,Foption was to ruin his life and nearly
OL,17,Ftake mine."
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@EO]rD@SOUwD@AOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780743771
OL,3,CMan jailed for 26 years for
OL,4,C'ferocious' knife attack on ex-partner
OL,5,Cat workplace
OL,7,FGiles Bedloe, prosecuting, told the
OL,8,Ftrial that Ashraf had become
OL,9,F"obsessed" with Ms Skeites and accused
OL,10,Fher of "cheating" on him despite the
OL,11,Frelationship having ended several
OL,12,Fmonths previously and Ms Skeites not
OL,13,Fbeing in a new relationship.
OL,15,FMr Bedloe said that on the morning of
OL,16,Fthe attack Ms Skeites was preparing
OL,17,Ffor a training presentation at the
OL,18,Ftravel agency where she worked when
OL,19,Fshe received a message that Ashraf was
OL,20,Foutside the building and had asked to
OL,21,Fsee her.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@JO]rD@HOUrD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780743771
OL,3,CMan jailed for 26 years for
OL,4,C'ferocious' knife attack on ex-partner
OL,5,Cat workplace
OL,7,FHe had "bombarded" her with 49 phone
OL,8,Fcalls before turning up at the
OL,9,Fpremises, and "circling in the
OL,10,Fshadows" as he waited to see Ms
OL,11,FSkeites.
OL,13,FHe said that Ms Skeites went to see
OL,14,Fhim and after a "brief conversation,
OL,15,Fshe told him to leave her alone and go
OL,16,Faway" before "randomly he hugged her"
OL,17,Fand he followed her back into the
OL,18,Flobby as she tried to move away from
OL,19,Fhim.
OL,26,@oD@HOUoD@RO]qD@OOUrD@HO]vD@QOUxD@EO]xD@
OL,26,ANOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780743771
OL,3,CMan jailed for 26 years for
OL,4,C'ferocious' knife attack on ex-partner
OL,5,Cat workplace
OL,7,FHe added: "She was telling him he
OL,8,Fneeded to leave. Suddenly he said 'I
OL,9,Fhave a knife' and showed her a black-
OL,10,Fhandled kitchen knife."
OL,12,FMr Bedloe said the victim later
OL,13,Fdescribed the attack saying: "Before I
OL,14,Fknew it, he was stabbing me".
OL,16,FThe prosecutor said that the defendant
OL,17,Fwas restrained by members of the
OL,18,Fpublic with one man kicking his legs
OL,19,Fto knock him over before blocking his
OL,20,Fexit.
OL,26,@oD@KOUrD@WO]uD@^OUvD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780743771
OL,3,CMan jailed for 26 years for
OL,4,C'ferocious' knife attack on ex-partner
OL,5,Cat workplace
OL,7,FThe court heard that Ashraf had a
OL,8,Fhabit of drinking a bottle of whisky
OL,9,For vodka each day and had gone to a
OL,10,Fretreat in India and to Dubai in bids
OL,11,Fto solve his drinking problem.
OL,13,FNick Tucker, defending, said that
OL,14,FAshraf, a father of two, had
OL,15,F"struggled" since being abused as a
OL,16,Fchild and suffered from depression.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1780743771
OL,3,CMan jailed for 26 years for
OL,4,C'ferocious' knife attack on ex-partner
OL,5,Cat workplace
OL,7,FHe said: "It was something of a mental
OL,8,Fhealth crisis, he had very little
OL,9,Fsleep in the week preceding the attack
OL,10,Fand his thinking had become rigid and
OL,11,Fobsessive and although he has not been
OL,12,Fformally diagnosed with any mental
OL,13,Fillness, all the evidence points to
OL,14,Fhim having some form of mental health
OL,15,Fcrisis."
OL,17,FHe added that Ashraf had "expressed
OL,18,Fremorse" for Ms Skeites' suffering
OL,19,Ffollowing the attack.
OL,26,@oD@JOUwD@HO]yD@ZOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/12
